name: realestate
description: The Real Estate Crypto Token (REAL ESTATE) aims to revolutionize the real estate market by combining blockchain technology with gamification, decentralized finance (DeFi), and accessibility. This token opens doors for small investors, gamifies real estate market participation, and provides unique opportunities to earn, trade, and stake. With REAL ESTATE, investors can access the profits of real property without the high entry costs traditionally associated with real estate
